{"tid":1647251,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"下星期一文化中心有《孤星淚》睇","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:53:38.000Z","uid":189861,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"441f1c02bb9bfc5238710db0f265dc28541cd4ad","tid":1647251,"uid":189861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />代傳～黎緊星期一晚Ponte Singers &amp; Orchestra有場《孤星淚》係文化中心做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Musical in Concert - Les Miserables <br />\nPonte Singers &amp; Orchestra 將會上演名劇：孤星淚<br />\n<br />\n日期 Date：2019年10月14日<br />\n時間 Time: 19:30<br />\n地點 Venue: 香港文化中心音樂廳 Concert Hall, Hong Kong Cultural Centre<br />\n<br />\n主要演員：<br />\n曾鈺棋 Freddie Tsang <br />\n劉榮豐 Rick Lau <br />\n符潤光 Raymond Fu <br />\n鄭君熾 Jordan Cheng<br />\n謝雅兒 Tse Nga-Yi <br />\n龐卓欣 Ada Pong<br />\n溫卓妍 Jarita Wan <br />\n林澤群 Pichead Amornsomboon<br />\n何敏兒 Jenus Ho </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>訂票: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/oxzmPPr6Ht46okVg9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FoxzmPPr6Ht46okVg9&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=caf2b40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/oxzmPPr6Ht46okVg9</a><br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最重要係最重要係最重要係</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地所有飛劃一每張$200，每售出一張就有熱心人士捐$100比星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />享受音樂劇之餘又可以幫到小朋友，何樂而不為呢？(唔好同人講入面有首Do you hear the people sing，萬一到時太多人一齊唱變咗非法集會就sad)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPish<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a687ae2fb4c0fdad1201ea185300af8fe8a129b","tid":1647251,"uid":67054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"諗起呢排<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uLwSK4-v8zA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuLwSK4-v8zA&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2f21bf6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uLwSK4-v8zA</a>"},{"pid":"f2b9ab1b5fa69a084deb5588337cb8b5505da8ef","tid":1647251,"uid":189861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1a687ae2fb4c0fdad1201ea185300af8fe8a129b","tid":1647251,"uid":67054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"諗起呢排<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uLwSK4-v8zA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuLwSK4-v8zA&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2f21bf6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uLwSK4-v8zA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"我睇過幾集（暴露年齡）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298654ffa634e81ac0786c7448bbd68d19508096","tid":1647251,"uid":275341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"tui tui tui <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntoi toi toi <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ccd75883388e3115206bb4786a66f23af3e963","tid":1647251,"uid":87657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"嘩 好睇，係呢個時候做，要罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki